OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FA group of business leaders were last
OL,7,Fnight telling me that they and their
OL,8,Fcustomers were postponing investment
OL,9,Fand spending decisions because of
OL,10,Funcertainties caused by the long wait
OL,11,Ffor the budget.
OL,13,FSome of that uncertainty was dispelled
OL,14,Fthis morning by the Chancellor Rachel
OL,15,FReeves in an unusual pre-budget speech
OL,16,Fto journalists in Downing Street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
