OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FThe nutshell of what she said was that
OL,7,Fthere is a hole in the public finances
OL,8,Fthat is much bigger than she expected
OL,9,Fin the spring, that it's not her fault
OL,10,F(I'll come back to that), and that she
OL,11,Fwill do what's in the national
OL,12,Finterest to fill the hole, not what's
OL,13,Fpolitically expedient.
OL,15,FShe said two other things that are
OL,16,Fhighly significant: that her
OL,17,Fpriorities are bringing down interest
OL,18,Frates for people and the government,
OL,19,Fand that her other priority is
OL,20,Fbringing down inflation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
