OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FWhat does this all mean?
OL,8,FFirst, she needs to find around #35
OL,9,Fbillion in additional taxes - because
OL,10,Fthe OBR's productivity and growth
OL,11,Fdowngrade will see forecast tax
OL,12,Frevenues evaporate to the tune of more
OL,13,Fthan #20 billion, and at least another
OL,14,F#15 billion needs to be found to cover
OL,15,Fstymied welfare savings, higher
OL,16,Fgovernment interest payments and an
OL,17,Fincrease in the fiscal cushion or
OL,18,F"headroom."
