OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FTo digress a moment, do take note of
OL,7,Fthis newfound prudence, which is
OL,8,Fdesigned to reassure bond investors
OL,9,Fand end the stigma that the British
OL,10,Fgovernment pays more to borrow than
OL,11,Fany comparable government.
OL,13,FSecond, she no longer feels
OL,14,Fconstrained by the promises in her
OL,15,Fmanifesto not to increase taxes on
OL,16,F"working people" (the implication of
OL,17,Fher answer to my question) because she
OL,18,Fcan't raise that much money
OL,19,Fefficiently without increasing VAT or
OL,20,Fthe basic rate of income tax.
