OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FA VAT rise is out of the question
OL,7,Fbecause it would lead to higher
OL,8,Finflation and interest rates (see
OL,9,Fabove).
OL,11,FSo, pretty much everyone, except those
OL,12,Fon the lowest incomes, needs to
OL,13,Fprepare to pay more income tax, from
OL,14,Fboth a probable 2p increase in the
OL,15,Fbasic rate and the freezing of the tax
OL,16,Fthresholds for another couple of years.
OL,18,FSo far, so painful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
