OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FBut although all of that flows from
OL,7,Fspeech, it's not why she gave the
OL,8,Fspeech.
OL,10,FHer motive was that she wanted to
OL,11,Fdemonstrate that there has been what
OL,12,Flawyers would call a "material adverse
OL,13,Fchange" in economic conditions, and
OL,14,Ftherefore that no right-thinking
OL,15,Fperson would expect her to honour
OL,16,FLabour's manifesto promises not to
OL,17,Fincrease the rates of the big taxes on
OL,18,Fpeople and businesses.
OL,20,FDid she succeed?
