OL,3,CIs Reeves to blame for looming income
OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FWell, she came across as anxious,
OL,7,Fwhich is hardly surprising given that
OL,8,Fbreaking a manifesto pledge,
OL,9,Fespecially on tax, is a big deal.
OL,11,FAnd she was on firmest ground when she
OL,12,Ftalked about the headwinds caused by
OL,13,FTrump's tariffs, the stickiness of UK
OL,14,Finflation and the exceptional
OL,15,Fvulnerability of the UK's public
OL,16,Ffinances.
OL,18,FWhere there is more dispute is her
OL,19,Fcontention that she can't be blamed
OL,20,Ffor the OBR's growth and productivity
OL,21,Fdowngrade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
