OL,4,Ctax rises?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis has two parts to it.
OL,13,FIt would be absurd to blame her for
OL,14,Fthe UK's lousy productivity over the
OL,15,Flong term, because that is largely the
OL,16,Ffault of the previous Tory
OL,17,Fgovernment's lamentable stewardship.
