OL,6,FShe may have inherited this problem.
OL,7,FBut it was glaringly obvious even
OL,8,Fbefore Labour won the election. For
OL,9,Fchancellor and prime minister to imply
OL,10,Fno one told them is a bit daft.
OL,12,FBut now that they do know, most of you
OL,13,Fwill presumably hope they do something
OL,14,Fabout it!
